  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the efficacy of a sequential regimen of 14 days in patients with catheter-related
      bacteremia by S. aureus methicillin-susceptible, selected based on a pre-established clinical
      and microbiological criteria.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
